# Shared secrets for all sites under LocalServerApps/.
# This file is gitignored. Add more keys here as new sites need them.

## Shab Train Clock
# MTA Bus API key — get one at https://register.developer.obanyc.com/
MTA_BUS_API_KEY=

## PSFC Monitor
# Your ort.foodcoop.com login credentials
PSFC_EMAIL=
